SUMMARY:Davis Forest School Summer Camp Registration - Davis
DESCRIPTION:Registration for Davis Forest School Summer Camps opens on Sunday\, March 1 at 8 am! \nLike our drop-off programs during the school year\, our summer camps offer a thoughtful blend of child-led exploration and play\, and facilitated activities\, including nature crafts\, nature awareness-based games and activities\, and naturalist studies. Each group brings a unique energy\, with varying abilities and desires\, so no two weeks will be exactly the same! \nThis summer we will have concurrent week-long day camps for 5-12 year olds at both the Putah Creek South Fork Preserve and the Putah Creek Riparian Reserve every week. All camps will run from 8 am to 2 pm\, with a flexible drop-off window from 8-8:30 am. Tuition is $310/week. \nWe also have several weeks of Little Coyotes Summer Camp for ages 3-6. Little Coyotes Summer Camp will run from 9 am to 2 pm\, with a flexible pick-up window from 1:30 pm – 2 pm\, and tuition is $310/week.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/davis-forest-school-summer-camp-registration-davis/2026-03-15/
