SUMMARY:Bohart Museum of Entomology Open House: Eight-Legged Encounters!
DESCRIPTION:Come and enjoy the fourth event in the UC Davis Bohart Museum of Entomology’s Weekend Open House series for 2025-2026. This free\, all ages event will be focusing on arachnids\, fascinating eight-legged arthropods. This includes animals such as spiders\, scorpions\, camel spiders\, vinegaroons\, tailless whip scorpions\, pseudoscorpions\, etc… Meet arachnid experts\, visit the Bohart research collection\, make crafts\, and have fun learning. This is a free event\, as is the parking.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/bohart-museum-of-entomology-open-house-eight-legged-encounters/
LOCATION:Bohart Museum of Entomology (Bohart Museum)\, 1124 Academic Surge\, UC Davis Campus
CATEGORIES:Bring the Kids,Community,Science
